    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken incredible care of it, and I promise you won't find a single scratch. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
