    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This specimen features the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) boxer-six, delivering 385hp with a linear power band and no IMS bearing concerns. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a limited-slip differential, ensuring surgical turn-in and corner-exit traction. Maintenance is comprehensive, including recent transaxle fluid service and a clean cylinder bore scope report. The factory paint retains its original luster with zero rock chips, and the cabin remains in showroom condition with no leather shrinkage or soft-touch plastic degradation. This is a mechanically superlative example for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
