    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero chips, swirls, or imperfections in the paint. Every panel is original, and the body lines are factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin retains that new-car scent; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, and all electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014always garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full folder of meticulous service records included. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, and the engine bay has been detailed to a professional standard. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of this model, perfect for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
