    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and always tucked away in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car markup, you\u2019ve found it. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
