    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is an exceptional example of Zuffenhausen engineering, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical vetting, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recent bore-scoring inspection with clean results. The suspension geometry is dialed in via Bilstein B16 coilovers, ensuring peak lateral grip and communicative chassis feedback. The engine remains bone dry with no weeping from the rear main seal. Finished in swirl-free Arctic Silver over a Supple Leather interior, this unit retains its factory-spec structural rigidity and crisp throttle response. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking mechanical perfection.",
